lst.str: He said commodity operations deputy administrator Ralph Klopfenstein is currently in the midwest on a speaking tour and will meet with ASCS oficials in Kansas City next week.

lst.name: sentence
lst.str: Sindt acknowledged that concern has been voiced that USDA's price differentials between the New Orleans Gulf and interior markets are not accurate because of higher than normal barge freight rates.

lst.name: sentence
lst.str: "We do not have current plans to make any major adjustments or changes in our pricing," said Bob Sindt, USDA assistant deputy administrator for commodity operations.
